mployment-duration hide-for-small\">November 2014 - April 2015</div>\r\n		<div class=\"large-9 columns employment-description\">\r\n			<div class=\"company-name\">Agency Oasis</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-title\">Developer</div>\r\n			<div class=\"small-12 columns employment-duration show-for-small\">November 2014 - April 2015</div>\r\n			<div title=\"job-description\">\r\n				As a member of a four person team at Oasis, my roles as a developer are diverse--estimating new features, prototyping pages according to design documents, coding backend functionality, building content management structure, planning, interacting with the clients, and more. Oasis uses Sitecore to build sites that are fully customizeable by the customer once built and our team uses .Net as the framework to interface with Sitecore.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"employment-entry\">\r\n		<div class=\"large-3 columns employment-duration hide-for-small\">August 2013 - October 2014</div>\r\n		<div class=\"large-9 columns employment-description\">\r\n			<div class=\"company-name\">Engauge</div>\r\n			<div class=\"job-title\">User Interface Developer</div>\r\n			<div class=\"small-12 columns employment-duration show-for-small\">August 2013 - October 2014</div>\r\n			<div title=\"job-description\">\r\n				Engauge is a full-service marketing and advertising agency that works on large-scale projects for worldwide clients. With Engauge, I build out sites according to design specifications, localize content for global sites, create custom Javascript code for interactive pieces, build web apps, and manage server deployment scripts.\r\n			</div>\r\n		</div>\r\n		<div class=\"clearfix\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"employment-entry\">\r\n		<div class=\"large-3 columns employment-duration hide-for-small\">May 2012 - August 2013</div>\r\n		<div class=\"large-9 columns employment-description\">\r\n			<div class=\"company-name\">So